des:
Flatter me Please
Jonathan Duhon's sense of humor.
It is a delightful break from the serious nature of Jonathan's content on life and relationships.
Ask Alexa to compliment your favorite people (or even yourself!) and she will choose from a list funny list of comments added by Jonathan Duhon
Another installment to The Me Please Collection from Jonathan Duhon

Tell me what you think at Jonathan@fixerme.com
